      <title>日本立法者称 Facebook 诈骗需要更严格的在线规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/facebook-scams-demand-stricter-online-rules-japan-lawmaker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[执政党数字推广工作组负责人表示，当 Meta Platforms Inc. 等公司未能解决社交媒体诈骗问题时，日本必须实施法律来更好地监管这些公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/facebook-scams-demand-stricter-online-rules-japan-lawmaker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 06:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
